                <h1>Your privacy matters.</h1>
                <p>Textora is a simple note-taking interface that does not collect personal data. Notes are saved on the server only to enable editing and retrieval by title.</p>
                <h2>What we do</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Store note content by title to let you open and update notes.</li>
                    <li>Serve static assets and pages without tracking personal behavior.</li>
                    <li>Use minimal metadata for site functionality only.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We do not use cookies for tracking, and we do not sell or share note content. If the app is deployed publicly, note access is controlled only by the title you use.</p>
